{"word":"κατασκευάζω","slug":"κατασκευάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰατασϰευάζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, σϰευάζω</el> ‘prepare, make ready’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘arrange proper conditions’, <b>prepare <a href='B:470 11:10'>Mt 11:10</a>; <a href='B:480 1:2'>Mk 1:2</a>; <a href='B:490 1:17'>Lk 1:17</a>.</b> Of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> made ready inwardly <b><a href='B:490 7:27'>Lk 7:27</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘erect a structure’, <b>build <a href='B:650 3:3'>Hb 3:3f</a>; <a href='B:650 11:7'>11:7</a>; <a href='B:670 3:20'>1 Pt 3:20</a>.</b> W. focus on construction for various purposes <b>construct <a href='B:650 9:2'>Hb 9:2</a>, <a href='B:650 9:6'>6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κατασκάπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κατασκηνόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}